<view class="page"><view class="card"><view class="title">{{assignment.title||'作业详情'}}</view><view>{{assignment.requirements}}</view><view class="muted">可以提交多张照片、文字、语音、短视频、PDF 或 Word；照片预检只提示，不自动判分。</view><button wx:for="{{assignment.attachments}}" wx:key="url" class="secondary" data-url="{{item.url}}" bindtap="openFile">{{item.wholePaper?'打开整张试卷':'打开附件'}}：{{item.name}}</button></view><button class="primary" bindtap="submit">提交或订正</button></view>
